extends ./ntu.msd.layout.jade

block title
  title Event

block content
  .wrapper
    .poster#poster-label
      .ps-img
        //- Replace this with the poster image found in your images/ntu.msd folder.
        img(src="../../img/15-16/ntu.msd/poster.photo.jpg")
        .ps-cover
    .ps-well
      .col-md-3
      .col-md-6
        h1 南洋理工大学大马运动会
        h3 Malaysian Sports Day @ NTU
        .btn.btn-dark.description-btn 
          h3 #活动详情
        a(href="ntu.msd.updates.html").white.btn.btn-dark.events-btn             
          h3 #近期更新
        :markdown
          Feeling tired of study? Wishing to make more friends? Looking for a break?
          Show us your sports talent! Ladies and gentlemen, hesitate no more and join us for Malaysian Sports Day 2016!

          For this year, we have basketball, dodgeball, futsal, frisbee and badminton games. And not to forget, 200m sprint for all the male sprinters and 4*100m mixed sprint relay (2 males and 2 females in one team)! Don’t miss this opportunity to grab them!

          Free MSD T-shirt and breakfast will be provided!

        a(href="ntu.msd.register.html").btn.btn-dark.btn-lg 
          h3 我要参加！


      .col-md-3

    .container.grey-bg.full-pg#description-label
      .row
        .col-md-3
        .col-md-6
          h1.border-bottom-light 活动详情
        .col-md-3
      .row
        .col-md-4
        .col-md-5.align-left
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-clock-o.red &nbsp;
            | 活动日期 : 
            //- Replace the following date with event date
            | 13th March 2016 
          h2 
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-calendar.yellow &nbsp;
            | 活动时间 : 
            //- Replace the following time with event time
            | 8am - 6pm
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-building.blue &nbsp;
            | 活动地点 : 
            span.fa.fa-magic
            //- Replace the following venue with event venue 
            | NTU Sports & Recreation Centre

          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-check.red &nbsp;
            | 报名截止日期 :  
            | 21st February 2016

        .col-md-3

